text: Abrosovo () is the name of several rural localities in Russia: *Abrosovo, Ivanovo Oblast, a village in Verkhnelandekhovsky District of Ivanovo Oblast *Abrosovo, Novgorod Oblast, a village in Pestovsky District of Novgorod Oblast *Abrosovo, Pskov Oblast, a village in Pskovsky District of Pskov Oblast *Abrosovo, Vladimir Oblast, a village in Petushinsky District of Vladimir Oblast
title: Abrosovo
